CREATE TABLE products_partition_1 PARTITION OF products FOR VALUES WITH (modulus 10, remainder 1);
-- ... more partitions up to 9 ...
Now, when we add a product, the database will automatically put it in the correct small table (partition) based on the customer ID.

Summary
By splitting our big table into smaller tables, we make it easier and faster to find and manage our products, just like dividing toys into smaller boxes makes it easier to play with them.

